song.title: Bouncin at 4pm
song.info:
this track is a remix of our "strollin' at 4am". that is also on this package. sometimes you feel that you' sat around for too long and that it's time to get up and shake your legs. so go on, why are you still sitting in front of your screen?
this track made 6th place at mekka 2001's fast forward compo.
